HOUSE BILL 1841
By Haston
SENATE BILL 1494
By Walley
AN ACT to amend Tennessee Code Annotated, Title 49,
Chapter 6, relative to student discipline.
BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 49-6-3402, is amended by deleting
"grades one through six (1-6)" wherever it appears in the section and substituting "grades one
through five (1-5)" and by deleting "grades seven through twelve (7-12)" wherever it appears in
the section and substituting "grades six through twelve (6-12)".
SECTION 2. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
